nsgress the commandment of God by your tradition?","year":32},{"id":"recGjCT90FE1bqIYt","ref":"Matt.15.4","text":"For God commanded, saying, Honour thy father and mother: and, He that curseth father or mother, let him die the death.","year":32},{"id":"rec3yDvngOLCnrxnx","ref":"Matt.15.5","text":"But ye say, Whosoever shall say to his father or his mother, It is a gift, by whatsoever thou mightest be profited by me;","year":32},{"id":"recuZS1BCMJzaKCJQ","ref":"Matt.15.6","text":"And honour not his father or his mother, he shall be free. Thus have ye made the commandment of God of none effect by your tradition.","year":32},{"id":"recI5bhUgFVU4qcAB","ref":"Matt.15.7","text":"Ye hypocrites, well did Esaias prophesy of you, saying,","year":32},{"id":"recTHU0zN29GPU2rr","ref":"Matt.15.8","text":"This people draweth nigh unto me with their mouth, and honoureth me with their lips; but their heart is far from me.","year":32}]}
